# Do not use !out/** here — it re-included out/**/*.map (source maps) into the VSIX.
# README.md, LICENSE, icon.png, syntaxes/, snippets/, language-configuration.json, bin/ — not listed = included
# Dependencies are bundled into out/extension.js (webpack); do not ship node_modules
# bin/ is INCLUDED — native onec-hbk-bsl for platform-specific release VSIX
